{"title":"Must Watch: Tom Pagès executes double front flip to base jump off 135m cliff in France","link":"https://bikerumor.com/must-watch-tom-pages-executes-double-front-flip-to-base-jump-off-135m-cliff-in-france/","date":1637246328000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><div data-off-canvas-content=\"\"><main><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/18093710/tom-pages-flight-mode-cliff-base-jump-mx-bike.jpg\" data-fancybox=\"\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"525\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/18093710/tom-pages-flight-mode-cliff-base-jump-mx-bike-800x525.jpg\" alt=\"tom pages cliff jump fmx basejump 135m avoriaz france\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/18093710/tom-pages-flight-mode-cliff-base-jump-mx-bike-800x525.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/18093710/tom-pages-flight-mode-cliff-base-jump-mx-bike-297x195.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/18093710/tom-pages-flight-mode-cliff-base-jump-mx-bike-120x79.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/18093710/tom-pages-flight-mode-cliff-base-jump-mx-bike-768x504.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/18093710/tom-pages-flight-mode-cliff-base-jump-mx-bike-1536x1008.jpg 1536w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/18093710/tom-pages-flight-mode-cliff-base-jump-mx-bike.jpg 1600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"></a><header></header><p>Support us! BikeRumor may earn a small commission from affiliate links in this article. <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/privacy\" target=\"_blank\">Learn more</a>.</p></main><main role=\"main\"><article id=\"post-278655\" role=\"article\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/BlogPosting\"><section itemprop=\"text\"><p>Yes, this is a motocross video, but I shan’t be apologetic for sharing. With the sheer guts involved in this maneuver, we can’t help but watch in awe as Red Bull Freestyle MX athlete, Tom Pagès, launches his moto off this 135m cliff, completing not one but two front flips before deploying a parachute. What about the bike?! Don’t worry, it got its very own parachute…</p><h2>Tom Pagès Flight Mode</h2><p><iframe loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1200\" height=\"675\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/ZvXE5rsfuZQ?version=3&amp;rel=1&amp;showsearch=0&amp;showinfo=1&amp;iv_load_policy=1&amp;fs=1&amp;hl=en-US&amp;autohide=2&amp;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation\"></iframe></p><p>There’s actually a 37 minute documentary about Tom’s preparation for the final trick on Red Bull – watch it <a href=\"https://www.redbull.com/int-en/films/flight-mode-by-tom-pages\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">here</a>.</p><p><a href=\"https://www.redbull.com/int-en/films/flight-mode-by-tom-pages\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><em>RedBull.com</em></a></p></section></article></main></div></div>","author":"Jessie-May Morgan","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"ba9cbd56491710cb94049b7c6803ab99256f3b41c0d52d2e674349640bcd956e","category":"Cycling"}